	restorecon
	man -l xx_selinux, eg. httpd_selinux

Use boolean settings to modify system SELinux settings
	sebool
	getsebool -a | grep whatever
	setsebool -P whateverbool on (DO NOT FORGET THE -P PERSISTENT)


